title: 1988–89 Scottish Cup
text: The 1988–89 <a href="Scottish%20Cup">Scottish Cup</a> was the 104th staging of Scotland's most prestigious <a href="Association%20football">football</a> knockout competition. The Cup was won by <a href="Celtic%20F.C.">Celtic</a> who defeated <a href="Rangers%20F.C.">Rangers</a> in the final.
